| data2 = Independently, [[Johannes Nicolaus Br<U+00F8>nsted]] and [[Martin Lowry|Thomas Martin Lowry]] formulated the idea that [[acid]]s are proton (H<sup>+</sup>) donors while bases are proton acceptors.
